Great lord, ……, @wDN{Nuska}, caretaker of the great gods, @wDN{Nuska}, prince respected in the @wTN{E-kur}, caretaker of ……! Youth who knows well how to give instructions, who …… decisions; trustworthy god who loves ……, who listens to prayers! When the shining @wTN{E-kur}, the shrine which assigns the divine powers, is made up as for a festival, and @wDN{Enlil} and @wDN{Ninlil} sit there attractively, may your pure mouth bring friendly words on behalf of @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}! Addressing them daily, may he be able to please them unto distant days! When the house of @wDN{Enlil}, the shrine which assigns the divine powers, is made up as for a festival, and @wDN{Enlil} and @wDN{Ninlil} sit there attractively, may your pure mouth bring friendly words on behalf of @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}! Addressing them daily, may he be able to please them unto distant days!

@(B.B.17 = 17-27) When he greets them in prayer and supplication, may they look favourably upon him! Assign him a good life, a good reign, and years of joy! May he be elevated to be prince of all the great lords of the south and the uplands! May he exercise forever the leadership of the living of all lands, the numerous people! May they look favourably upon @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}, son of @wDN{Enlil}! Assign him a good life, a good reign, and years of joy! May he be elevated to be prince of all the great lords of the south and the uplands! May he exercise forever the leadership of the living of all lands, the numerous people! …… @wDN{Nuska} ……. May you be his ……!
